# ==========================================
# GITHUB IGNORE LIST - SECURITY & PRIVACY
# ==========================================

# 1. Environment Variables
.env

# 2. Nginx Proxy Manager Data & Configurations
# CRITICAL: Contains SQLite databases, domains, and access/error logs
data/

# 3. SSL Certificates
# CRITICAL: Contains highly sensitive Let's Encrypt Private Keys
letsencrypt/

# 4. Backups and Temporary Files
*.bak
*.tmp
